## Code Snippets and Context

### Polygon Data Fetcher Initialization

```python
class PolygonDataFetcher(DataFetcher):
    def __init__(self, data_lake_handler: Optional[DataLakeHandler] = None):
        api_key = os.getenv('POLYGON_API_KEY')
        if not api_key:
            raise ValueError("API key for Polygon is not set in environment variables.")

        super().__init__(
            api_key=api_key,
            base_url='https://api.polygon.io/v2/aggs/ticker',
            source='Polygon',
            data_lake_handler=data_lake_handler,
            raw_csv_dir='C:/TheTradingRobotPlug/data/polygon/raw',
            processed_csv_dir='C:/TheTradingRobotPlug/data/polygon/processed',
            db_path='C:/TheTradingRobotPlug/data/trading_data.db',
            log_file='C:/TheTradingRobotPlug/logs/polygon.log',
            env_file='C:\TheTradingRobotPlug\.env'
        )
```

